asset.value: Now let's gather {{returns.IRS1040.Return.ReturnData.IRS1040.DependentWorksheetPP._CURRENT_.PossessiveRelationshipLabel}} Social Security number

We just need {{returns.IRS1040.Return.ReturnData.IRS1040.DependentWorksheetPP._CURRENT_.PossessiveRelationshipLabel}} Social Security number to get you that ${{returns.IRS1040.Return.ReturnData.PPReturnInformation.SpouseExemptAmountPP}} deduction.
This number may help you get other deductions and credits that reward you for taking care of {{returns.IRS1040.Return.ReturnData.IRS1040.DependentWorksheetPP._CURRENT_.RelationshipLabel}}.
[[M0]]This feature isn't ready yet.[[/M0]] But we'll still remember to get this info from you later, so it's OK to move on.
What if I don't have this Social Security number?
